  + [finding_002_higher_rank_source_gap] is higher analytic rank needs source families beyond repeated rank-one Heegner points
    = meaning: the R-hand "growth" side must become a construction of enough independent classes, not just a traversal metaphor
    = proof_status: open_for_general_BSD
  + [finding_003_control_gap_shift] is higher-rank Euler, Kolyvagin, and Stark systems sharpen upper control once suitable systems exist
    = meaning: they can help prevent hidden extra rank, but they are not a universal source constructor
    = proof_status: conditional_or_special_setting
  + [finding_004_best_revelation_corridor] is special higher-cycle or diagonal-cycle settings are the best next place to seek meaning
    = meaning: they keep all three desired roles visible: source object, regulator or p-adic height measurement, and Euler-system-style control
    = proof_status: promising_as_structural_research_not_solution

